  "doc_id": "55748",
  "text": "Stakeholder theory is a useful perspective for addressing important issues in business [CITATION_1] . These authors further maintain that this theory is effective in that stakeholders that are well taken care of tend to reciprocate with a positive attitude towards the business. Stakeholder theory involves attending to the interests and well-being of all business stakeholders [CITATION_2] . Hence, this theory's purpose is to create value not only for business owners but for stakeholders as well. Thus, stakeholder theory is drawn on in this article to show how it could be relevant to understanding tourism SMMEs' stakeholders within social media environments.",
